# multi-functional MCP-devtools server over SSE <br> [ğŸŒ¸ ãƒªãƒ¼ãƒ‰ãƒŸãƒ¼](https://github.com/daoch4n/mcp-devtools/blob/main/%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89%E3%83%9F%E3%83%BC.MD) [ğŸ® è¯»æˆ‘](https://github.com/daoch4n/mcp-devtools/blob/main/%E8%AF%BB%E6%88%91.MD)

